  "texts": [
    "4.2) and examine the impact of the proxy capability by using various base models for proxy training (Sec. 4.3).",
    "Experiment We evaluate the effectiveness of our approach on extensive preference datasets.",
    "We use Llama-2 7B (Touvron et al., 2023) for both the target and proxy base model.",
    "Following Rafailov et al. (2023), we first conduct supervised finetuning (FT) with their prompts and chosen responses (preferred-FT) to boost DPO training.",
    "We train the finetuned model with the DPO objective (Eq. 2) on both the subset D c and the full dataset D p for comparison."
